snippet.title: Two Furry Vampires take on the Dragon Hordes of Dundalk - Zorro and Zedd Steam Trailer
snippet.description: Zorro and Zedd fight the Dragon knights and Lords to gain an audience with Octobatron, the Dragon King. Guided by the Goddess Mallary, they intend to take back their homeland for all bat-kind.
